metadata.name: Cloudy's Genius Interview
metadata.description:
I didn't wanna be here, Genius asked me to be here. 

I got a text that said, "yooo do you want to come talk about your music?" 

I said "nah." 

But they kept calling!

My manager also kept texting me saying how she thought it would be great PR. 

SO I folded, I'm sorry. 

Here's that interview I never wanted to do in the first place. With Genius. Enjoy.
